2017-04-27 16:49:09,336 ERROR [ThreadPoolAsyncTaskExecutor::Thread 10] [spring.scanner.extension.ComponentImportBeanFactoryPostProcessor] postProcessBeanFactory Unable to load class 'com.atlassian.jira.config.properties.ApplicationProperties' for component importation purposes.  Skipping...
 -- referer: http://localhost:8090/setup/evallicense.action | url: /setup/setupembeddeddb-default.action | traceId: 00589699d0685ef4 | userName: anonymous | action: setupembeddeddb-default
{code}

h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Start Confluence Server 6.1.x

